482
0:19:14.26,000 --> 0:19:16,000
And I have to tell you,

483
0:19:16.26,000 --> 0:19:18,000
it was energizing.

484
0:19:18.26,000 --> 0:19:2,000
It connected deeply with something in me

485
0:19:20.26,000 --> 0:19:22,000
about identity,

486
0:19:22.26,000 --> 0:19:25,000
about the capacity of every person to contribute

487
0:19:25.26,000 --> 0:19:27,000
to a community, to a perspective that is hopeful.

488
0:19:27.26,000 --> 0:19:29,000
Well I went into the courtroom.

489
0:19:29.26,000 --> 0:19:31,000
